  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover “Will Jump”, a captivating platform game that plunges you into a retro universe full of challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Will, an intrepid locksmith and hero who comes running with his keys. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to overcome 23 thrilling levels spread over 6 unique biomes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its “die & retry” gameplay, every attempt will bring you closer to victory or a nervous breakdown. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into this pixelated adventure and take on the challenge of conquering every platform!</p>",
